<h4 id="toc1"><span>简述</span></h4>
<p>只需引用一次：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-source]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<p>可重复引用：</p>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-top</span><br />
|trans= <span class="no-sel">决定书架在手机屏幕下是否横排，填yes或no</span><br />
|list-shelf= <span class="no-sel">书架编号</span><br />
|book-annotation= <span class="no-sel">决定书籍采取A类还是B类注释，填1或2，不填则无</span><br />
]]</p>
<p><span class="no-sel">重复引用下方组件即可重复排列书籍：</span><br />
<em><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-books</span><br />
|self-defining=false<br />
|book-cover= <span class="no-sel">封面颜色，见预设样式，填对应英文</span><br />
|link-color= <span class="no-sel">链接颜色，见预设样式，填对应英文</span><br />
|book-link= <span class="no-sel">链接地址</span><br />
|link-name= <span class="no-sel">链接文本</span><br />
|book-info= <span class="no-sel">注释在此</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></em></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-bottom]]</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<h4 id="toc2"><span>复制用</span></h4>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-source]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-top</span><br />
|trans=yes<br />
|list-shelf=0<br />
|book-annotation=1<br />
]]</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-books</span><br />
|self-defining=false<br />
|book-cover=green<br />
|link-color=gold<br />
|book-link= <span class="no-sel">链接地址</span><br />
|link-name= <span class="no-sel">链接文本，<strong>限11个汉字</strong>。</span><br />
|book-info= <span class="no-sel">注释在此</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-books</span><br />
|self-defining=false<br />
|book-cover=red<br />
|link-color=gold<br />
|book-link= <span class="no-sel">链接地址</span><br />
|link-name= <span class="no-sel">链接文本</span><br />
|book-info= <span class="no-sel">注释在此</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
