<div id="u-ch1"></div>
<div class="tt-ch ch-1">
<div class="tt-line-top tt-{$self-line}"></div>
<div class="tt-txt">
<h1 id="toc3"><span>介绍</span></h1>
<p><span class="sub-tt">{$sub-title}</span></p>
</div>
<div class="tt-line-bottom tt-{$self-line}"></div>
</div>



<div class="txt-1">
<p>该组件可模拟书架与其上书籍样式，适用于搭配图书馆版式或者营造相近的气氛，总之多多少少能令页面美观。不过不建议添加太多书籍，以免造成页面卡顿。</p>
<p>要使用该组件，请按下列步奏进行：</p>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div id="u-ch-1-1"></div>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc4"><span>一：引用源代码</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<p><br />
<strong>该代码在一个页面只需要添加一次。</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>[[include :scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-source]]</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br /></p>
<p><br /></p>
<hr />
<div id="u-ch-1-2"></div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc5"><span>二：封装书架</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<p><br /></p>
<h4 id="toc6"><span>1. 添加以下代码</span></h4>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-top</span><br />
|trans=yes<br />
|list-shelf=1<br />
|book-annotation=1<br />
]]</p>
<p>书籍添加处</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-bottom]]</span></p>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<h4 id="toc7"><span>2. 选择自定义内容</span></h4>
<div class="help">
<blockquote>
<p>include组件代码块的起始，<strong>需完整地黏贴在开头</strong> ↦</p>
<p>书架的编号，添加此可更好与其他书架区别 ↦</p>
<p><strong>必填</strong>，书架是否会在手机屏幕下改为横排<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup> ↦</p>
<p>书籍额外信息展示形式<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-2')">2</a></sup> ↦</p>
<p>是否使用自定义隔板样式<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup> ↦</p>
<p>自定义隔板背景色 ↦</p>
<p>自定义隔板背景覆盖样式 ↦</p>
<p>自定义隔板滤镜 ↦</p>
<p>自定义隔板边框 ↦</p>
<p>自定义隔板边框裁角 ↦</p>
<p>结束引用块 ↦</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-top</span></p>
<p>|list-shelf= 1</p>
<p>|trans= yes / no</p>
<p>|book-annotation= 1 / 2 / 其他则无</p>
<p>|my-plank=yes</p>
<p>|plank-background=</p>
<p>|plank-background-size=</p>
<p>|plank-filter=</p>
<p>|plank-border=</p>
<p>|plank-border-radius=</p>
<p>]]</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;复制用</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;复制用</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-top</span><br />
|list-shelf=<br />
|trans=<br />
|book-annotation=<br />
|my-plank=yes<br />
|plank-background=<br />
|plank-background-size=<br />
|plank-filter=<br />
|plank-border=<br />
|plank-border-radius=<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
<p>书籍在此。</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-bottom]]</span></p>
</div>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<p><strong>附记：</strong>若要在书架外套外框以看起来更像书架（见下方示例一二），可如此：</p>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[div&#32;class=&quot;et-out-bookrack&quot;]]</span></strong><br />
<strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[div&#32;class=&quot;et-inner-bookrack&quot;]]</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-top</span><br />
|trans=yes<br />
|list-shelf=1<br />
|book-annotation=1<br />
]]</p>
<p>书籍在此</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-shelf-bottom]]</span></p>
<p><strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span></strong><br />
<strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span></strong></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div id="u-ch-1-3"></div>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc8"><span>三：添加书籍</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<p><br /></p>
<h4 id="toc9"><span>1. 复制以下基本代码：</span></h4>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-books</span><br />
|book-cover= <span class="no-sel">封面颜色，见预设样式</span><br />
|link-color= <span class="no-sel">链接颜色，见预设样式</span><br />
|book-link= <span class="no-sel">链接地址</span><br />
|link-name= <span class="no-sel">链接文本，<strong>限11个汉字</strong>。</span><br />
|book-info= <span class="no-sel">注释在此</span><br />
|self-defining= <span class="no-sel"><strong>必填</strong>。是否启用自定义样式，可能值：false / true ；</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<h5 id="toc10"><span>封面颜色，预设值</span></h5>
<div style=" column-width:15px; column-gap:10px; column-rule:1px #333 double; column-rule-width:2px; column-count:3;">
<ol>
<li>red</li>
<li>gold</li>
<li>green</li>
<li>black</li>
<li>galaxy</li>
<li>purple</li>
<li>mix-2</li>
<li>mix-1</li>
<li>blue-2</li>
<li>blue</li>
<li>darkblue</li>
<li>blue-3</li>
<li>darkblack</li>
<li>white</li>
<li>darkgrey</li>
</ol>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<h5 id="toc11"><span>链接颜色，预设值【按示例一二的顺序排列】</span></h5>
<p><br /></p>
<div style=" column-width:15px; column-gap:10px; column-rule:1px #333 double; column-rule-width:2px; column-count:4;">
<ol>
<li>gold</li>
<li>red</li>
<li>white</li>
<li>black</li>
</ol>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<h5 id="toc12"><span>样式效果见下方示例一二，<a href="#u-ch2">点此跳转</a></span></h5>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;复制用</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;复制用</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-books</span><br />
|book-cover=<br />
|link-color=<br />
|book-link=<br />
|link-name=<br />
|book-info=<br />
|self-defining=false<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<h4 id="toc13"><span>2. 自定义选项：</span></h4>
<p><br /></p>
<h5 id="toc14"><span><strong>注意，使用自定义选项会覆盖预设值，但没有启用对应的自定义选项的话，可以保留预设值相关选项，以避免样式缺省。</strong></span></h5>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="help">
<blockquote>
<p>include组件代码块的起始，<strong>需完整地黏贴在开头</strong> ↦</p>
<p>书本的编号，以区别其他自定义书籍样式 ↦</p>
<p>封面样式，预设值 ↦</p>
<p>链接颜色，预设值 ↦</p>
<p>链接地址 ↦</p>
<p>链接文本 ↦</p>
<p>补充信息 ↦</p>
<p><strong>是否启用自定义样式，填true则继续填以下选项 ↦</strong></p>
<p>自定义书籍描边<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-4')">4</a></sup>，填色码 ↦</p>
<p>自定义书籍封面，填背景相关值<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-5')">5</a></sup> ↦</p>
<p>自定义书脊<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-6" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-6')">6</a></sup> ↦</p>
<p>自定义链接颜色 ↦</p>
<p>自定义A类注释<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-7')">7</a></sup>文本颜色 ↦</p>
<p>自定义B类注释<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-8" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-8')">8</a></sup>阴影 ↦</p>
<p>自定义B类注释背景 ↦</p>
<p>自定义B类注释边框 ↦</p>
<p>结束引用块 ↦</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-books</span></p>
<p>|list-book=0</p>
<p>|book-cover=</p>
<p>|link-color=gold</p>
<p>|book-link=#</p>
<p>|link-name=链接文本</p>
<p>|book-info=注释在此</p>
<p><strong>|self-defining=true / false</strong></p>
<p>|self-book-color=#162c44</p>
<p>|self-book-background=url(&quot;xxx&quot;)</p>
<p>|self-book-border=2px solid #320f79</p>
<p>|self-link-color=red</p>
<p>|self-description-color=</p>
<p>|self-info-shadow=rgba(9,9,9,0.5)</p>
<p>|self-info-background=rgba(9,9,9,0.5)</p>
<p>|self-info-border=5px inset #333</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<h5 id="toc15"><span>效果见下方的示例三，<a href="#u-ch3">点此跳转</a></span></h5>
<p><br /></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;复制用</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;复制用</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="blockquote">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki-cn:component:bookshelf-books</span><br />
|list-book=<br />
|book-cover=<br />
|link-color=<br />
|book-link=#<br />
|link-name=链接文本<br />
|book-info=注释在此<br />
<strong>|self-defining=true</strong><br />
|self-book-color=<br />
|self-book-background=<br />
|self-book-border=<br />
|self-link-color=red<br />
|self-description-color=<br />
|self-info-shadow=<br />
|self-info-background=<br />
|self-info-border=<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div id="u-ch2"></div>
<div class="tt-ch ch-2">
<div class="tt-line-top tt-{$self-line}"></div>
<div class="tt-txt">
<h1 id="toc16"><span>示例一二</span></h1>
<p><span class="sub-tt">横排样式、书架样式、颜色样式、注释样式</span></p>
</div>
<div class="tt-line-bottom tt-{$self-line}"></div>
</div>



<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded" style="display:none"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;显示书架示例</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;隐藏书架示例</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><br /></p>
<div class="et-out-bookrack">
<div class="et-inner-bookrack">
<div id="u-ch-2-1"></div>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://scpsandboxcn.wdfiles.com/local--files/etinjat-2/Liber.jpg" width="130px" alt="Liber.jpg" class="image" />
<h3 id="toc17"><span>示例一</span></h3>
<h5 id="toc18"><span>手机时不横排，及在横栏上显示额外信息【A类注释】</span></h5>
</div>



<div class="shelf-1 shelf-wrap trans-no my-plank-{$my-plank}">
